snippet.title: Reversed Rebecca - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The RPG game where your choices really matter! 
Steam page : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2297990/Reversed_Rebecca/ 

Find tools, solve puzzles, go back in time and reverse causality! But beware of the consequences... 

Learn more : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=70TemnSfeqQ&list=PLYWafroUWU5V25ie9wy8NzFz3AwhMrZrT 

Music by danosongs.com
